{"tid":810672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美婦車禍服抗生素 舌頭竟長滿毛茸茸黑毛","createTime":"2018-09-08T07:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T08:11:07.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1692ad518d50e3f44a171307a442598ec88b5541","tid":810672,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"美婦車禍服抗生素 舌頭竟長滿毛茸茸黑毛<br />\n<br />\n2018-09-08 10:51<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國一名55歲婦人去年遭遇嚴重車禍，因傷口感染而服用抗生素，不料一週後竟出現舌頭長滿「黑毛」的狀況，求診後發現罹患罕見「黑毛舌」（black hairy tongue）疾病，負責此病例的醫師也直呼「自己執業10年首度遇上」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《新英格蘭醫學期刊》（New England Journal of Medicine）週四（6日）刊登這份病例，指女患者2017年經歷一場嚴重車禍，雙腳遭壓斷且發生感染，醫師遂開給她2種抗生素同時服用以抵抗病菌。不料，女子開始服藥一週後便出現黑毛舌症狀，口腔更出現無法言喻的臭味。<br />\n<br />\n女子不堪其擾，便向美國聖路易斯華盛頓大學醫學院內科學系助理教授哈馬德（Yasir Hamad）求助，後者懷疑患者服用的其中一種抗生素－米諾環素（Minocycline）是致病成因，便要求她停止服藥並注意口腔衛生，此後數週女子傷勢痊癒，舌頭上的「黑毛」亦全數消失。<br />\n<br />\n黑毛舌雖名為「黑毛」，但從患者舌頭上生長出的毛狀物體卻不是毛髮，而是舌上絲狀乳頭異常延伸增長，其表面呈現黑色。異常增長的舌乳頭經常刺激軟顎，常引起噁心感，同時導致患者出現明顯的口腔異味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2544941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2544941&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fx0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3ef2255e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2544941&h=da2fcdaa\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2544941</a>"},{"pid":"d073974a3f9afb14d150603fbdf3870358e1b37e","tid":810672,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/151555_00857aca86511e8ec746b2c0d1a8a342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F151555_00857aca86511e8ec746b2c0d1a8a342.jpg&h=a2072207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/151555_401a470267e90c94a7b0963938844c3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F151555_401a470267e90c94a7b0963938844c3c.jpg&h=6dde8f5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5285536fe1de543c554b8218d899548c2f869bac","tid":810672,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"條脷有毛"},{"pid":"427000ae22fd66b0f1a37967cd7a4f4cf8c8eb9d","tid":810672,"uid":100449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"電光毒龍鑽"}]}